border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ea3 penalty oan nghi\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Bernabeu t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 san b\u1eb1ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch thua 0-3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Michael Oliver b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Mehdi Benatia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Lucas Vazquez trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Gianluigi Buffon sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maradona to Lucas Vazquez cua Real an va kiem penalty hinh anh\" title=\"Maradona t\u1ed1 Lucas Vazquez c\u1ee7a Real \u0103n v\u1ea1 ki\u1ebfm penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Maradona-to-Lucas-Vazquez-cua-Real-an-va-kiem-penalty-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Buffon v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Oliver</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, Cristiano Ronaldo b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Wojciech Szczesny ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t cho Real tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Los Blancos ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. Theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra, Real s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Bayern \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Maradona tr\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Diego Maradona \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u1eeba qua. \u00d4ng \u0111\u1eb7t nghi v\u1ea5n Lucas Vazquez c\u1ee7a Real \u0103n v\u1ea1 trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng b\u1ed5 sung r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty kh\u00f4ng \u01b0? Kh\u00f4ng!\u201d, Maradona n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cSau khi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u, Vazquez ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 v\u00ec b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 Buffon v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb1ng sau c\u00f3 Benatia. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ng\u00e3 ra, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vazquez kiem penalty cho Real\" title=\"Vazquez kiem penalty cho Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/maradona-to-vazquez-cua-real-an-va-giong-het-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Maradona c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn Vazquez c\u1ee7a Real \u0103n v\u1ea1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/gap-real-thuyen-truong-bayern-mo-ve-chuc-vo-dich-champions-league-184-184191.html\">G\u1eb7p Real, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Bayern m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bayern-vs-real-ban-ket-champions-league-hum-buon-ken-ken-cung-chang-vui-gi-184-184184.html\">Bayern vs Real b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League: H\u00f9m bu\u1ed3n, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng vui g\u00ec</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-boc-tham-ban-ket-champions-league-201718-18h00-ngay-134-372-184166.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18: Bayern \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-mua-tien-dao-karim-benzema-197-184153.html\">Benzema c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<d