 class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Roma</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18 \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho ra hai c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Bayern Munich b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Liverpool vs AS Roma. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u01a1i h\u1ee5t h\u1eabng b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e3 mong \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft trong m\u01a1 gi\u1eefa Real v\u00e0 Bayern.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh hai c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n. Liverpool v\u00e0 Roma, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Barcelona l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao song h\u1ecd c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah phat bieu truoc tran Liverpool vs Roma hinh anh\" title=\"Salah ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Salah-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-Liverpool-vs-Roma-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Roma t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Salah h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Mohamed Salah r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Sau 44 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp ghi t\u1edbi 39 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh. Salah ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Roma cho th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi CLB c\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRoma l\u00e0 CLB c\u0169 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i y\u00eau c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng y\u00eau t\u00f4i\u201d, Salah n\u00f3i v\u1edbi CNN. \u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m vui \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah Man City vs Liverpool\" title=\"Salah Man City vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/truoc-dai-chien-salah-bay-to-tinh-yeu-voi-roma.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Roma \u0111\u1ea7y h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh trong 2 n\u0103m v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian vui v\u1ebb trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. T\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Francesco Totti. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Francesco, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng t\u1ed1t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/salah-roma-khong-muon-gap-liverpool-184-184186.html\">Salah: Roma kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-salah-172-184115.html\">Klopp b\u00e0ng quan v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a sao kh\u1ee7ng Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/doi-lai-cong-bang-harry-kane-bi-doi-thu-salah-mia-mai-172-184083.html\">\u0110\u00f2i l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, Harry Kane b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Salah m\u1ec9a mai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tieu-diet-man-city-salah-lai-duoc-so-sanh-voi-messi-184-184005.html\">Ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Man City, Salah l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-hung-salah-noi-gi-sau-khi-giai-cuu-liverpool-o-etihad-184-183990.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Salah n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Liverpool \u1edf Etihad?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1164","checkdouble":"184210"},{"date":"09:32 14/04","title":"Barcelona vs Valencia (21h15 ng\u00e0y 14/4): Li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c gi\u1ea3m nh\u1eb9 n\u1ed7i \u0111au","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/barcelona-vs-valencia-21h15-ngay-144-lieu-thuoc-giam-nhe-noi-dau.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration