 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League di\u1ec5n ra, ai ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i Roma \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t hay v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Barca kh\u00e1c xa ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Barca gi\u1eef th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League. Nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Roma 3-0 Barca c\u00f9ng n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n v\u00f4 t\u1eadn. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra t\u1eeb c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 h\u00fat ch\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla (h\u00f2a 2-2 sau khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 2-0) v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Leganes 3-1 ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Lionel Messi (l\u1eadp hat-trick).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh tran dau Barca vs Valencia vong 32 La Liga hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Nhan-dinh-tran-dau-Barca-vs-Valencia-vong-32-La-Liga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, Barca g\u1eb7p v\u00f4 v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Roma ch\u01a1i pressing t\u1ea7m cao v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Blaugrana v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, Barca k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. M\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, ph\u00eda Roma \u0111\u00e3 phong t\u1ecfa s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Barca r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng. Khi m\u00e0 Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o anh c\u0169ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f4ng c\u00f9n, th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb khai th\u00e1c tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3, Barca \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma. Qua \u0111\u00f3, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia b\u1ecb h\u1ea5t v\u0103ng ra kh\u1ecfi Champions League. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi n\u00f3, \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0103n 3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Pep Guardiola v\u00e0 Luis Enrique c\u1ee7a Valverde c\u0169ng tan bi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde\" title=\"HLV Valverde\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/hlv-valverde-chi-ra-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1ec1 \u201ct\u1eafm ao\u201d La Liga</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ecb Roma lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Valverde. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Barca ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng s\u1eeda sai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, li\u1ec7u Barca c\u00f3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hay kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. Valencia \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ec5 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t. 9 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i La Liga trong v\u00f2ng 2 th\u00e1ng qua, B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 8 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Atletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChu\u1ed7i phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Valencia v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real Madrid chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH La Liga. M\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t trong t\u1ed1p 4 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m tay, c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch x\u1ee9 Castellon c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Barca vs Valencia\" title=\"Preview Barca vs Valencia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Preview-Barca-vs-Valencia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga 21h15 ng\u00e0y 14/4</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Barca \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Valencia c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd t\u1edbi may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Mestalla m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00fat 60 \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. Ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Messi, Jordi Alba m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, gi\u00fap Barca ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Valencia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 c\u00e1ch Roma th\u1eafng vang d\u1ed9i Barca c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc kinh nghi\u1ec7m. B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng phong t\u1ecfa Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i La Liga, Valencia ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\nV\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng Barca l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd may m\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u00e0nh tinh kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. V\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Valencia v\u1eabn l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 thi d\u00f9 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nBarcelona (4-4-2):</strong> 1.Stegen - 20.Roberto, 3.Pique, 23.Umtiti, 18.Alba - 14.Coutinho, 5.Busquets, 4.Rakitic, 8.Iniesta - 10.Messi, 9.Suarez.<br>\r\n<strong>Valencia (4-4-2):</strong> 13.Neto - 3.Vezo, 24.Garay, 5.Gabriel, 14.Gaya - 18.Soler, 16.Kondogbia, 10.Parejo, 7.Guedes - 19.Rodrigo, 9.Zaza.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Barca 1-0 Valencia<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Barca vs Valencia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Barca vs Valencia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Barca-vs-Valencia-(deu-4-4-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-30-barca-thay-hen-nhat-tro-tra-gia-184-184180.html\">Roma 3-0 Barca: Th\u1ea7y h\u00e8n nh\u00e1t, tr\u00f2 tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bon