i-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League v\u1edbi Liverpool tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Man City kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi 2 ph\u00fat c\u1ee7a Gabriel Jesus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec The Citizens l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 san b\u1eb1ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch thua 0-3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ederson 2 l\u1ea7n sau nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a &ldquo;song s\u00e1t&rdquo; Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino. Qua \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-12-liverpool-song-nho-toc-do-chet-vi-toc-do-184-183994.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City b\u1ecb Liverpool lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League</strong></span> v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh tran dau Tottenham vs Man City vong 34 NHA hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs Man City v\u00f2ng 34 NHA h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Nhan-dinh-tran-dau-Tottenham-vs-Man-City-vong-34-NHA-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Leroy Sane \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Liverpool nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn. HLV Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o. Theo chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n, c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, Man City c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u00e1ch b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3, ngay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac Liverpool r\u01a1i v\u00e0o r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n na n\u00e1 nh\u01b0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/du-am-tran-man-city-23-mu-172-183777.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i Man City 2-3 Man United</strong></span> cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Guardiola c\u0169ng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n song l\u1ea1i ch\u00f9ng xu\u1ed1ng \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng tr\u1eafng tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Man City v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ef1a nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc th\u0103ng hoa nh\u01b0ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ec7u r\u00e3 v\u00e0 mong manh. Liverpool v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng quen thu\u1ed9c, song Man City th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City 1-2 Liverpool\" title=\"Man City 1-2 Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Truoc-vong-34-Premier-League-201718-Dia-nguc-chua-dut-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City \u0111ang ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u1edbi Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 Champions League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool (2 l\u1ea7n) v\u00e0 M.U. V\u00e0 th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft h\u1ecd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs Man City v\u00f2ng 34 NHA. Trong khi N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd th\u00ec Tottenham l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t l\u00ean ch\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League, Tottenham t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho Premier League v\u00e0 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch l\u00ean t\u1edbi 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham danh bai Chelsea 3-1\" title=\"Tottenham \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea 3-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/Nhan-dinh-Tottenham-vs-Man-City-vong-34-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham \u0111ang kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i Premier League</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Man City. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Spurs c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 song s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Man City l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110ang trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i, Man City li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i pressing t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Liverpool hay tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 M.U, HLV Guardiola c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Tottenham vs Man City\" title=\"Preview Tottenham vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-ngay-hom-nay-1442018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs Man City v\u00f2ng 34 NHA 1h45 ng\u00e0y 15/4</h2>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u1ea3 hai y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Wembley, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 10 trong s\u1ed1 12 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i t\u1edbi nay t\u1ea1i Premier League (h\u00f2a 2). \u0110\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd \u1edf \u0111\u1eb1ng sau, hi\u1ec7n Spurs \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i &ldquo;th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba&rdquo; Wembley.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng trong 2 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2-0 v\u00e0 4-1. T\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 7 n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mauricio Pochettino s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i t\u00e1i l\u1eb7p l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nTottenham (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Lloris - 24.Aurier, 6.Sanchez, 5.Vertonghen, 33.Davies - 15.Dier, 19.Dembele - 23.Eriksen, 20.Alli, 7.Son - 10.Kane.<br>\r\n<strong>Man City (4-3-3): </strong>31.Ederson - 2.Walker, 4.Kompany, 30.Otamendi, 18.Delph - 17.De Bruyne, 8.Gundogan, 21.D.Silva - 20.B.Silva, 33.Jesus, 19.Sane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Tottenham 2-1 Man City<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Tottenham vs Man City\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Tottenham vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Tottenham-vs-Man-City-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs Man City v\u00f2ng 34 NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man Cit