d-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hai t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Angel Gomes \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Man United hi\u1ec7n nay. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Angel Gomes:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2016/11/12/ANGEL-GOMES-\u272d-MAN.-UTD-\u272d-THE-SUPER-TALENT-\u272d-Skills-&-Goals-2016.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf FA Cup m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Angel Gomes g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Yeovil Town v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Tahith Chong v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 U23. Thi tho\u1ea3ng sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Carrick tien cu hai sao tre cho Mourinho hinh anh\" title=\"Carrick ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed hai sao tr\u1ebb cho Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/carrick-tien-cu-2-sao-tre-cho-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Carrick ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed hai sao tr\u1ebb cho Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Carrick \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Gomes v\u00e0 Chong</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/michael-carrick-chinh-thuc-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-172-181918.html\" target=\"_blank\">Carrick s\u1ebd gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Man United</span> m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cL\u00fac n\u00e0y Man United \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Rashford, Shaw, Lingard, Martial v\u00e0 Lukaku. \u1ede h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n, Man United c\u00f2n hai t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Angel Gomes v\u00e0 Tahith Chong.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao-172-184092.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/11/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao-172-184092.html\">Man United ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sao tr\u1ebb Rashford</span><br>\r\n<span>L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Manchester United m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford. Theo \u0111\u00f3, MU kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Rashford d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c v\u00ec c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 h\u1ecd ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1t th\u00e1o v\u00e0 x\u00f4 x\u00e1t v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1ecf neo, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec. Hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u00edch cho t\u00f4i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Carrick kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho Man United. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed7i khi ra s\u00e2n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 Man United:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-144-man-city-run-so-truoc-mu-184-184189.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 14/4: Man City run s\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-voi-herrera-172-184187.html\">MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Herrera</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/inter-milan-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-sao-bu-real-176-184172.html\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u1ee5 sao b\u1ef1 Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-buon-vu-sao-fulham-172-184148.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 sao Fulham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rio-ferdinand-muon-mu-chieu-mo-sao-real-madrid-172-184095.html\">Rio Ferdinand mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-khong-ban-rashford-voi-bat-cu-gia-nao-172-184092.html\">Man United ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sao tr\u1ebb Rashford</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1160","checkdouble":"184206"},{"date":"07:49 14/04","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 17h00 ng\u00e0y 14/4 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/14/nhan-dinh-shb-da-nang-vs-ha-noi-17h00-ngay-144-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Reg