a s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o v\u00f2ng 34: &ldquo;Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t danh hi\u1ec7u, t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc sang th\u00e1ng 11, 12, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Man City m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep lo ngai kha nang Man City vo dich Premier League hinh anh\" title=\"Pep lo ng\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/pep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League \u0111ang b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Man United r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. MU c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong tay nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 thua 3 tr\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 1 tu\u1ea7n. Man City c\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Pep Guardiola cho bi\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<h2>H\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00eam nay, Man City s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Wembley, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t, b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. T\u1ea1i Premier League, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u1ebfp theo, Pep s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/4. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Spurs, s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i cho ng\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng quang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-vong-34-premier-league-dia-nguc-chua-dut-172-184178.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/truoc-vong-34-premier-league-dia-nguc-chua-dut.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-vong-34-premier-league-dia-nguc-chua-dut-172-184178.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League: \u0110\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c ch\u01b0a d\u1ee9t</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4i, Man City x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n l\u00fac n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18, s\u1ebd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-lieng-xieng-jesus-yeu-cau-man-city-guong-day-172-184176.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/thua-lieng-xieng-jesus-yeu-cau-man-city-guong-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-lieng-xieng-jesus-yeu-cau-man-city-guong-day-172-184176.html\">Thua li\u1ec3ng xi\u1ec3ng, Jesus y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Man City g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9c c\u00f4 c\u1ea7u b\u1ea1i&rdquo; \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, Man City \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1158","checkdouble":"184193"},{"date":"07:30 14/04","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Hazard s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea