\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i Champions League m\u00f9a sau qua TV.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh tan \u0111\u00e0n x\u1ebb ngh\u00e9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte c\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V, r\u1eb1ng anh c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Top 4 ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec hay ho&rdquo; &ndash; ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 chia s\u1ebb. &ldquo;B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Champions League h\u00e0ng n\u0103m, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Top 4.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dau hieu cho thay Eden Hazard o lai Chelsea hinh anh\" title=\"D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Eden Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/haz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong Top 4, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ebb v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.&rdquo; &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Trong 2 th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a&rdquo; &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec chia s\u1ebb, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Eden Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, khi anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7 Hazard chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bay-khoi-top-4-conte-do-loi-cho-hoc-tro-172-184190.html\">Bay kh\u1ecfi Top 4, Conte \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/morata-bao-chua-cho-mua-giai-te-hai-o-chelsea-172-184151.html\">Morata b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-tien-courtois-bo-chelsea-toi-psg-172-184149.html\">V\u00ec ti\u1ec1n, Courtois b\u1ecf Chelsea t\u1edbi PSG?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-khuyen-chelsea-ban-cau-thu-thay-vi-sa-thai-conte-172-184147.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khuy\u00ean Chelsea gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Conte v\u00e0 b\u00e1n 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dang-le-chelsea-nen-giu-lai-diego-costa-172-184060.html\">\u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd Chelsea n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Diego Costa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/fan-west-ham-nem-do-choi-nguoi-lon-vao-khung-thanh-chelsea-188-184023.html\">Fan West Ham n\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1157","checkdouble":"184194"},{"date":"08:32 14/04","title":"Southampton vs Chelsea (18h30 ng\u00e0y 14/4): Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng ch\u01b0a d\u1ee9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/doi-hinh-du-kien-southampton-vs-chelsea-18h30-ngay-144-khung-hoang-chua-dut.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-