ground-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch r\u1ec7u r\u00e3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, The Blues gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n v\u1ecb th\u1ebf xu\u1ed1ng ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o Top 4. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho r\u1eb1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea s\u1ebd \u1edf nh\u00e0 xem Champions League qua TV l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, <strong>h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111ang lo\u2026 Arsenal c\u01b0\u1edbp m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5.</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u1ecdi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n FA Cup l\u00e0m c\u1ee9u c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u00ean th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111ang n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 c\u1ea3 th\u1ea7y l\u1eabn tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra, Chelsea v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, h\u1ecd g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Antonio Conte c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 v\u1ecdng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb (Callum Hudson-Odoi), r\u00fat Morata ra ngh\u1ec9 khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f4i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea5t n\u00f3i l\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Conte v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh Southampton vs Chelsea vong 34 Premier League hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Southampton vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Nhan-dinh-Southampton-vs-Chelsea-vong-34-Premier-League-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 bay kh\u1ecfi Top 4</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4 gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Conte s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1 l\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Chelsea ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac c\u1ea7n l\u1eafm m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng d\u00e0i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, c\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng Conte bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, sau khi t\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9. Nh\u1eefng Emerson, Drinkwater, Zappacosta, Barkley \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 FA Cup khi \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Southampton, v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ngay v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League t\u1ed1i nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u201c\u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Southampton vs Chelsea (18h30 ngay 144) Khung hoang chua dut hinh anh 2\" title=\"Southampton vs Chelsea (18h30 ng\u00e0y 144) Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng ch\u01b0a d\u1ee9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/4/Southampton-vs-Chelsea-(18h30-ngay-144)-Khung-hoang-chua-dut-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p nhau</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary's c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00f3p ng\u00f3p \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, v\u1edbi chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda, v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 9 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 coi th\u01b0\u1eddng The Saint sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i Emirates tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi g\u00e2y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Soton th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a khi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111ang l\u00e0 2-1 cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. Tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Mark Hughes. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 Chelsea, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua cho su\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Southampton vs Chelsea\" title=\"Preview Southampton vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Preview-Southampton-vs-Chelsea.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Southampton vs Chelsea di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n nay, Southampton v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 1 tr\u1eadn trong tay v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf. Nghe th\u1eadt l\u1ea1 l\u00f9ng, khi <strong>m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0\u2026 \u0110KV\u0110</strong>. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u00ec Soton ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Chelsea \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, c\u1ea3 2 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nhau t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft FA Cup. V\u00e0 tr\u00ean SV\u0110 St Mary's t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Southampton vs Chelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1eadp 1 c\u1ee7a \u201c\u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1<br>\r\n</strong> \u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Southamton th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n, trong 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Southampton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1 trong 4 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn St Mary's.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 trong 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea thua 3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n</strong> \u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Stephens s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i do nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Sam McQueen v\u00e0 Steven Davis g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean ph\u00eda Chelsea, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Zappacosta, Luiz v\u00e0 Barkley.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Southampton vs Chelsea\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Southampton vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Southampton-vs-Chelsea-(4-2-3-1-vs-3-4-2-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Southampton vs Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Southampton vs Chelsea: </strong>2-2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-hazard-se-o-lai-chelsea-172-184194.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Hazard s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bay-khoi-top-4-conte-do-loi-cho-hoc-tro-172-184190.html\">Bay kh\u1ecfi Top 4, Conte \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/morata-bao-chua-cho-mua-giai-te-hai-o-chelsea-172-184151.html\">Morata b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-tien-courtois-bo-chelsea-toi-psg-172-184149.html\">V\u00ec ti\u1ec1n, Courtois b\u1ecf Chelsea t\u1edbi PSG?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bi-west-ham-cam-hoa-dieu-toi-te-nhat-con-chua-den-172-183839.html\">Chelsea b\u1ecb West Ham c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a: \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1156","checkdouble":"184200"},{"date":"19:13 13/04","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-4 N\u1eef H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 20h45 ng\u00e0y 13/4 (VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/8/link-xem