ea5n kh\u1edfi khi b\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e1 th\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u1edf nh\u1ea5t, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t so v\u1edbi hai \u201cth\u00fa d\u1eef\u201d th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Real Madrid. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1eadp t\u1eaft t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i gay g\u1eaft khi t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool vs Roma ban ket C1 HLV Klopp de chung doi thu hinh anh\" title=\"Liverpool vs Roma b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 HLV Klopp d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/klopp-nghi-roma-de-tho-cho-liverpool-thi-that-het-thuoc-chua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool vs Roma b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 Champions League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c sau k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Liverpool vs Roma b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1: \u201cT\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y: \u2018\u01a0n ch\u00faa kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Bayern Munich!\u2019 hay \u2018\u01a0n ch\u00faa kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Real Madrid!\u2019, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Roma l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ebft thu\u1ed1c ch\u1eefa. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho anh ta \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c<em><strong>Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh ta kh\u00f4ng xem </strong></em><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/barca-bi-roma-loai-khoi-champions-league-khong-dep-khong-co-quyen-184-184089.html\"><em><strong>hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Roma tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barcelona</strong></em></span><em><strong> r\u1ed3i</strong></em>. H\u1ecd thua 1-4 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111\u00fang di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, n\u00f3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c th\u00ec h\u1ecd thua thi\u00ean t\u00e0i Messi. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f3, tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Barca \u0111\u1ebfn 4-0 hay 5-0 r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Roma l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League sau k\u1ef3 t\u00edch l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barcelona v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f9ng Liverpool t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C\u00fap C1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u0103m 1984. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Roma b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h45 c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 25/4 \u1edf Anfield (l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i) v\u00e0 3/5 \u1edf Olimpico (l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Liverpool vs Roma r\u1ed3i, th\u1ebf c\u00f2n Si\u00eau Kinh \u0110i\u1ec3n Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid th\u00ec sao?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-c