px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mo Salah ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t s\u00e2n Anfield. 37 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng gi\u1edd nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 cho kh\u00f4ng, Liverpool ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n r\u1ed1i r\u00edt AS Roma, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18, v\u00ec m\u00f3n h\u1eddi n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban ket Liverpool vs Roma Salah noi gi khi tai ngo doi bong cu hinh anh\" title=\"B\u00e1n k\u1ebft Liverpool vs Roma Salah n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/salah-roma-khong-muon-gap-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u00f4i sao Salah s\u1edbm t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Roma b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Salah, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi Roma ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed3i sinh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh qua hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf Serie A. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m Liverpool vs Roma:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Rome s\u1edbm nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, n\u01a1i t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau qu\u00fd b\u1edfi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong CLB c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec Liverpool ch\u1ee9.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Jurgen Klopp m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0ng ng\u1ee3i khen Roma sau nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh ban \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Roma: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cMo c\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Roma. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eebng l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Th\u1eed t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Roma v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Mo xem, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfn xa \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u n\u1eefa?\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bayern-vs-real-ban-ket-champions-league-hum-buon-ken-ken-cung-chang-vui-gi-184-184184.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/bayern-vs-real-ban-ket-champions-league-hum-buon-ken-ken-cung-chang-vui-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bayern-vs-real-ban-ket-champions-league-hum-buon-ken-ken-cung-chang-vui-gi-184-184184.html\">Bayern vs Real b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League: H\u00f9m bu\u1ed3n, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng vui g\u00ec</span><br>\r\nSau g\u1ea7n 1 n\u0103m, Bayern Munich l\u1ea1i t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Real Madrid t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out Champions League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Bayern vs Real b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 xem ra ch\u1eb3ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn ni\u1ec1m vui...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-vs-as-roma-tai-ban-ket-champions-league-hoang-tu-tro-ve-184-184183.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/liverpool-vs-as-roma-tai-ban-ket-champions-league-hoang-tu-tro-ve.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-vs-as-roma-tai-ban-ket-champions-league-hoang-tu-tro-ve-184-184183.html\">Liverpool vs Roma b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League: Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed tr\u1edf v\u1ec1</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd, ch\u00ednh Mohamed Salah c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i CLB c\u0169 nhanh \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady, trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c gi\u1eefa Liverpool vs Roma.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nGia Khoa (TTVN)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1152","checkdouble":"184186"},{"date":"05:51 14/04","title":